Native LLVM build tools for LLVM @LLVM_VERSION@.

This prefix is a workflow bootstrap artifact, not a distributable target SDK.
It is built on the GitHub Actions Linux x86_64 runner and reused by target
matrix jobs to avoid rebuilding same-version native LLVM helper tools for every
target.

Bootstrap LLVM version: @BOOTSTRAP_LLVM_VERSION@
LLVM targets: @LLVM_TARGETS@
LLVM experimental targets: @LLVM_EXPERIMENTAL_TARGETS@

Included tools:
  llvm-tblgen
  llvm-config
  llvm-nm
  llvm-readobj
